			<P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="border: none; padding: 0cm; font-weight: medium">
			Auto Place All &ndash; If this is checked, the game with
			automatically select territories for you during the territory
			selection phase. Note, some game types will automatically select
			territories for you.</P>
			<P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="border: none; padding: 0cm; font-weight: medium">
			Auto End Go &ndash; If this is checked the turn will end
			automatically once you have ended or carried out a Fortify
			Position move, however, you will not be able to use the Undo
			feature, this allows for faster game play. Leaving this option
			unchecked will allow use of the Undo feature.<BR><BR>
